11#include "ipf.h"
12#include "kmem.h"
13
14int kmemcpywrap(from, to, size)
15 void *from, *to;
16 size_t size;
17{
18 int ret;
19
20 ret = kmemcpy((caddr_t)to, (u_long)from, size);
21 return ret;
22}
